    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/17bb8f8b84f576722cfa336e0f29b79d.avif?t=1749365600\" width=300 height=162 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Death Delivery》是一款快节奏的 FPS 动作游戏，您可以慢速进行，从许多令人惊叹的体验中汲取灵感，这是街机乐趣，您可以快速跳入其中并开始享受纯粹的乐趣，享受华丽的视觉效果和令人满意的效果。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                           难以掌握</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/7b1f6996fd1638b4d23a5effe41b4294.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲进不间断的动作关卡，一次都不会被击中……是的，一次，因为你一枪毙命！，残酷的试错难度确保你掌握游戏机制，并享受无穷乐趣它是一款快速且高度可重玩的令人满意的动作游戏，向 2000 年代的经典动作游戏致敬。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                          风格自由</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/4c5c9611183a2ba777248ef8578e433c.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按你的方式玩！将枪战、近战、手臂、腿和慢动作结合起来，发挥你的创造力，获得最佳体验并获得最佳分数来解锁新关卡。这很难，但租枪的生活也是如此。你能胜任这项任务吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.poster.avif?t=1749365600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.webm?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303790/extras/1fdaf7b379f5c67a4fbae0d2eee75b00.mp4?t=1749365600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
